# Verification Plan

## Setup
1. cd /home/user/myproject
2. npm install
3. node index.js &  # Wait for server to start on port 3000

## Verification Steps
1. **Create User**:
   - Request: POST http://localhost:3000/users
     Body: {"name": "Alice"}
   - Expected: Status 201, response includes {"id": number, "name": "Alice"}
   - Save the returned `id` as `user_id`.
2. **Create Product**:
   - Request: POST http://localhost:3000/products
     Body: {"title": "Laptop"}
   - Expected: Status 201, response includes {"id": number, "title": "Laptop"}
   - Save the returned `id` as `product_id`.
3. **Create Image for User**:
   - Request: POST http://localhost:3000/images
     Body: {"url": "http://example.com/alice.jpg", "imageableId": user_id, "imageableType": "user"}
   - Expected: Status 201, response includes {"id": number, "url": "http://example.com/alice.jpg", "imageableId": user_id, "imageableType": "user"}
   - Save the returned `id` as `user_image_id`.
4. **Create Image for Product**:
   - Request: POST http://localhost:3000/images
     Body: {"url": "http://example.com/laptop.jpg", "imageableId": product_id, "imageableType": "product"}
   - Expected: Status 201, response includes {"id": number, "url": "http://example.com/laptop.jpg", "imageableId": product_id, "imageableType": "product"}
   - Save the returned `id` as `product_image_id`.
5. **Get User with Images**:
   - Request: GET http://localhost:3000/users/{user_id}
   - Expected: Status 200, response includes `profilePictures` array containing an object with `url: "http://example.com/alice.jpg"`.
6. **Get Product with Images**:
   - Request: GET http://localhost:3000/products/{product_id}
   - Expected: Status 200, response includes `productPhotos` array containing an object with `url: "http://example.com/laptop.jpg"`.
7. **Get User Image with Polymorphic Association**:
   - Request: GET http://localhost:3000/images/{user_image_id}
   - Expected: Status 200, response includes an `imageable` object with `name: "Alice"`.
8. **Get Product Image with Polymorphic Association**:
   - Request: GET http://localhost:3000/images/{product_image_id}
   - Expected: Status 200, response includes an `imageable` object with `title: "Laptop"`.
